---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  description="Our privacy policy will help you understand what information is collected and how it is used."
  title="Privacy policy Â· ODY Spatial"
>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-12">
    <div class="prose prose-gray lg:prose-xl">
      <h1 class="mb-8 text-3xl font-bold">Privacy Policy</h1>

      <p class="text-zinc-600 mt-4 text-sm"><strong>Last Updated:</strong> January 2, 2025</p>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">1. Introduction</h2>
        <p>
          Welcome to Ody Spatial ("we," "our," or "us"). We are committed to protecting your
          personal data and privacy in compliance with the Singapore Personal Data Protection Act
          (PDPA). This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, disclose, and protect your
          personal information.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">2. Information We Collect</h2>

        <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-medium">2.1 Information You Provide</h3>
        <ul class="mb-6 list-disc pl-6">
          <li>Name and contact information (email address, phone number)</li>
          <li>Booking preferences and appointment details</li>
          <li>Payment information (processed through Polar.sh)</li>
          <li>Any additional information you provide during consultations</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-medium">2.2 Automatically Collected Information</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
          <li>Device information (IP address, browser type)</li>
          <li>Website usage data</li>
          <li>Cookies and similar technologies</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">3. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use your personal information for:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
          <li>Processing your booking requests through Cal.com</li>
          <li>Managing payment transactions through Polar.sh</li>
          <li>Communicating about your appointments and services</li>
          <li>Improving our website and services</li>
          <li>Complying with legal obligations</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">4. Third-Party Service Providers</h2>

        <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-medium">4.1 Cal.com</h3>
        <ul class="mb-6 list-disc pl-6">
          <li>Handles appointment scheduling</li>
          <li>Stores booking information</li>
          <li>For details about Cal.com's data handling, please visit their privacy policy</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 class="mb-3 text-xl font-medium">4.2 Polar.sh</h3>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
          <li>Processes payments</li>
          <li>Handles transaction data</li>
          <li>For details about Polar.sh's data handling, please visit their privacy policy</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">5. Data Storage and Security</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
          <li>We implement appropriate security measures to protect your data</li>
          <li>Personal information is stored on secure servers</li>
          <li>We retain your data only for as long as necessary</li>
          <li>Third-party providers may store data internationally</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">6. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>Under the PDPA, you have the right to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc pl-6">
          <li>Access your personal data</li>
          <li>Correct any inaccurate personal data</li>
          <li>Withdraw consent for data collection and use</li>
          <li>Request data deletion (subject to legal requirements)</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">7. Data Protection for Children</h2>
        <p>
          We do not knowingly collect information from individuals under 18 years of age without
          parental consent.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">8. Updates to Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>
          We may update this Privacy Policy periodically. Changes will be posted on this page with
          an updated revision date.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="mb-12">
        <h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl font-semibold">10. Governing Law</h2>
        <p>
          This Privacy Policy is governed by Singapore law and the Personal Data Protection Act
          2012.
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
<style>
  .prose {
    max-width: 65ch;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }

  .prose h1 {
    color: #1a1a1a;
  }

  .prose h2 {
    color: #2a2a2a;
    margin-top: 2rem;
  }

  .prose p {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .prose ul {
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .prose li {
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }
</style>
